climbs.name: Brady Law Sux
climbs.fa: Jim "Frodo" Lybarger, Dan Briley, Mike Sweet, Tom Ray

content.description: Friction climbing on a brown streak left of the small dihedral that goes partway up the center of the slab. Belay with gear. Walk/scramble off either side to descend.
content.location: The first brown streak left of the water polished section.

content.description: The middle of the Paiute Crags where the drainage off the hillside comes down by a long, low overhang. The right side is white water polished rock and the left is brown with desert varnish. Separated from the north Paiute Crags by a broken overlap/low-angle section and from the south Paiute Crags by a small gully/low-angle section.
